Description_lang: When you cast Avenger's Shield, you gain an absorb effect equal to ${$m1/10}.1% of your maximum health for $185676d.

description_blz.en_US: When you cast Avenger's Shield, you gain an absorb effect equal to 5.0% of your maximum health for 10 sec.

description_blz.de_DE: Nach dem Einsatz von 'Schild des Rächers' erhaltet Ihr einen Schild in Höhe von 5,0% Eurer maximalen Gesundheit, der 10 Sek. lang anhält.

description_blz.ko_KR: 응징의 방패를 사용하면 10초 동안 최대 생명력의 5.0%에 해당하는 피해 흡수 효과가 부여됩니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 當你施放復仇之盾時，你將獲得相當於生命力上限5.0%的傷害吸收效果，持續10秒。
